Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.37,0:01:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快滾 狗崽子們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.75,0:01:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城裡沒聽人說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一帶很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是何人?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.47,0:01:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下一介旅行者 名叫托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心迷了路…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛 我是多明妮卡·斯考達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命之恩 感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若雙頭犬去而復返就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來我家暫避片刻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭疼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要從這種傢伙手裡奪遺體啊

Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝鎧龍的願望

Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為領主 守備卻這麼鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有裝鎧龍在 哪還需其他的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她本人身手也不容小覷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然已經打過照面 就不能用奇襲作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住宿 請求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安眠 入浴 懇求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒忘記自己的目的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集遺體的事呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.76,0:02:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得 當然記得 忘卻 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼看都是忘了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驚愕 變身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是裝鎧龍的魔法嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 能問下你們之間是什麼關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 果然要問這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我們是兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且雖然是血脈相通的兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻墜入了禁斷之戀的愛河
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 這種背德行為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人親屬自然不會允許
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越受反對 燃燒越旺的戀愛之火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 越燒越烈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊地 熊熊地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死也不願分開的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:04:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾一度想到殉情而死 下輩子再長相廝守
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因最終沒能死成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改變想法 轉為手牽手私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而為了甩脫追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明知這森林危險 卻毅然選擇了穿過它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁斷之戀嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若有機會 我也想嘗試一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁斷之戀?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 在躲過追兵前儘管留在我這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯與阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁斷之戀 我毫不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別聽她瞎說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們雖是兄妹 但沒有血緣關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在同一個村落長大而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這沒什麼好招待的 但房間可自由使用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有種被人監視的討厭感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來她很是喜歡自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 一直沒看到別人的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她獨自住在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微探察一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嘉依卡 你先待在這兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨自 守候 不可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛骨悚然 恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有使用過的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有食材
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連老鼠都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 實在不像是領主過的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻燈機嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也太自戀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓 存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓 不戒備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是沒找到其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連裝鎧龍也不見蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡 剛才借用過龍的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼龍應該也在這附近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潛伏在宅子某處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若真的不在 對我們來說也是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 你打算怎麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明所以 解釋請求
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我準備先用正攻法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面請求她讓出遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若拒絕 則動用武力奪取
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒意見吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從雙頭犬救出 宿處提供
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡好人 戰鬥否定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武力行使 不好 恩將仇報
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒說錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你是不是忘了很重要的一點?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡可是你的殺父仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方是怎樣的大善人 處於怎樣的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都和我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目的 是實現你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做法由我來想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但採用與否 是僱主你的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你若這樣優柔寡斷 我們會很難辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tenmu An Gulv NIyaf Oul Alou 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加熱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Boiler
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡可是你的殺父仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯正確 我錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 遺體 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中 錯綜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡 恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 戰鬥 不喜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜘蛛網終於取乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長和我都是亂破師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 對主人所言是絕對服從的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已知 情報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長滿心只為實現主人嘉依卡的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才逼你做出抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決不是故意在為難你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想請你理解這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要潑熱水了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知是否合您的胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我的戎馬生涯可並不短
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舌頭沒有那麼嬌貴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽聞領主大人您是龍騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何沒見到您的裝鎧龍?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它有事離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你們來說 也是好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若有龍在身邊走來走去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必也是提心吊膽的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實比較可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 我有一件事想詢問您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您應是擊斃賈茲皇帝的八英雄之一吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那您應該持有他的遺體吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否將其讓給我?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼想要那個?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了實現重要之人的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是…你的目的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實現她的目的 就是我的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本就覺得你不像尋常百姓了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我確實持有皇帝的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要就打倒我奪走它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也正好在尋找戰鬥的對手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs43\shad0\pos(640,660)}重要之人…重要之人…重要之人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs43\shad0\pos(640,660)}重要之人…重要之人…重要之人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 擅自引發戰鬥是我不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也是無可奈何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你一時半會兒下不了決心與她一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可若在這裡浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好那個叫基烈特的騎士會追上我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊? 不是因為我沒等你而在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否 否定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於戰術…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長你更喜歡胸小 沒腰沒屁股的平板身材嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不懂兄長你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才說的重要之人 只是修辭而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀紫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又出來個別的女人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡給予了我目的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給予了我這技藝毫無用武之地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行屍走肉般等死的前亂破師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論她有意無意 我很承她這份恩情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛的告白?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是就不能注意點聽人說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 昨晚的事 道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「武力行使 不好 恩將仇報」的發言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也該說對不起 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我話說得有點太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那擬定下戰略吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時可開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們或許會收不住手殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能先把遺體位置 告訴我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不著擔心 就憑你們殺不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到中庭的幻燈機了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是說映出你樣子的那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堂堂正正來分個勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為鋼也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼故不怯 鋼故不惑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦逢敵 盡無一切躊躇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為滅此兇器也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵血轉化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡不對勁?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那傢伙才不是多明妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若真是八英雄之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼對嘉依卡活著毫不驚訝?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿巴爾特伯爵當時可是大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡的魔法探查 結果如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法探查 宅邸內 有大傢伙 存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宅子內我們都搜遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我說她有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:14:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無需第二劍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起 容不得絲毫大意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來那傢伙的能力 肉體即使受傷也可立即修復
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝鎧龍的魔法嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要害是額頭 看準這裡下手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過單單刺進去 沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不像挖削一樣破壞腦部 我都可以復原
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼輕易告訴我沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你就算知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起初我以為你只是個自戀狂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但看你現在的表現 我沒猜錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想假裝人類裝到幾時?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的多明妮卡到哪兒去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰爭結束就離開了你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你大概是被遺棄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此還是忘不掉曾並肩作戰的多明妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以像這樣 過著被主人包圍的生活?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可悲!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡有錯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 潛入其中帶來苦痛者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Intruder
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是你的真實面貌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人們想要的「我的面貌」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算開始生效了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身體已經動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉給你下的毒 正一點一點起效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種東西 休想對我有用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利刃呀奔流吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Ripper
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為人也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要害在額頭對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的多明妮卡去哪兒了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你殺的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…是病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰爭的終結改變了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了目標的多明妮卡 被病魔輕易帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我獨自留了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打仗時 被那般渴求的裝鎧龍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今已沒人再需要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想忘記曾經需要我的多明妮卡的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:19:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡直到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是抱著渴望戰鬥的心情死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你也渴望戰鬥?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想實現多明妮卡的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是這變成了你的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何不了結我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場戰鬥 殺你並非目的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照約定 遺體我們收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,講實話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在想今後該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話 還是想有個「活著的意義」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我決定把「殺死你」定為我新的目標!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 剛才的「多明妮卡」現在請叫「芙蕾多妮卡」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且先幫你把傷給治了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了以後能堂堂正正地打敗你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這豈不是說 我們之前的對話全都被你偷聽到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 貓 無罪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可這貓就是芙蕾多妮卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且為什麼想殺我的傢伙也一起坐在這兒啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.29,0:21:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同行者 增員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅途快樂 倍僧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡 同伴 加入
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝鎧龍最強 底氣倍增
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 芙蕾多妮卡 自由奔放
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾消失 一人旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周 第五集 「追逐者 受追逐者」


